### 1. Simple Python script (command‑line)

```python
#!/usr/bin/env python3

def main():
    print("Hello, world!")
    name = input("Enter your name: ").strip()
    if not name:
        print("You didn't type a name.")
    else:
        print(f"Nice to meet you, {name}!")

if __name__ == "__main__":
    main()
```

